$","div",null,{"className":"blog-aside-card","children":[["$","strong",null,{"data-i18n":"blog.aside.title","children":"Need a recommendation?"}],["$","span",null,{"data-i18n":"blog.aside.text","children":"Send your target application, country and quantity. TOKNAV can recommend a suitable product or solution package."}],["$","a",null,{"href":"/inquiry","children":[["$","span",null,{"data-i18n":"cta.sendRequirements","children":"Send Your Requirements"}]," ",["$","$L2",null,{"iconNode":"$0:rsc:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:props:children:0:props:children:3:props:children:1:props:iconNode","className":"lucide-arrow-right","size":16}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"blog-aside-card muted-card","children":[["$","strong",null,{"data-i18n":"blog.more","children":"More guides"}],[["$","$L12","how-to-choose-rtk-gnss-receiver-surveying-construction",{"href":"/blog/how-to-choose-rtk-gnss-receiver-surveying-construction","children":"How to Choose an RTK GNSS Receiver for Surveying, Mapping and Construction Projects"}],["$","$L12","gnss-auto-steering-machine-control-buying-guide",{"href":"/blog/gnss-auto-steering-machine-control-buying-guide","children":"GNSS Auto-Steering and Machine Control: A Practical Buying Guide for Precision Agriculture Dealers"}]]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"blog-content","children":[["$","h2","0",{"children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Introduction"}]]}],["$","p","2",{"children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"RTK positioning depends on correction data. Without a suitable correction setup, even a strong GNSS receiver cannot deliver stable centimeter-level results in the field. For many buyers, the question is not whether they need RTK, but how they should provide corrections: a local base-rover setup, a CORS network, a VRS service, or a hybrid system."}]]}],["$","p","4",{"children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"This question appears often in procurement discussions because each setup has different costs, operating requirements and application advantages. A surveying company may prefer a portable base-rover workflow for remote jobs. A city-level mapping project may need CORS infrastructure. A precision agriculture dealer may need correction access for many machines across a region. A deformation monitoring project may require continuous data, reliable antennas and long-term system stability."}]]}],["$","p","6",{"children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"This article compares CORS/VRS and base-rover RTK from a practical B2B perspective. It explains how the systems work, where they fit, what equipment is usually required and what buyers should prepare before requesting a quotation."}]]}],"$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31","$L32","$L33","$L34","$L35","$L36","$L37","$L38","$L39","$L3a","$L3b","$L3c","$L3d","$L3e","$L3f","$L40","$L41","$L42","$L43","$L44","$L45","$L46","$L47","$L48","$L49","$L4a","$L4b","$L4c","$L4d","$L4e","$L4f","$L50","$L51","$L52","$L53","$L54","$L55","$L56","$L57","$L58","$L59","$L5a","$L5b","$L5c","$L5d","$L5e","$L5f","$L60","$L61","$L62","$L63","$L64","$L65","$L66","$L67","$L68","$L69","$L6a","$L6b","$L6c","$L6d","$L6e","$L6f","$L70","$L71"]}]]}]]}]
